# Browsers that we support for modern e-commerce website

# Production: Modern browsers only
> 1%
last 2 versions
not dead

# No support for legacy browsers
not ie <= 11
not op_mini all

# Modern features support
supports es6-module
supports es6-module-dynamic-import

# Mobile browsers (e-commerce friendly)
iOS >= 14
Android >= 8

# Modern desktop browsers
Chrome >= 90
Firefox >= 88
Safari >= 14
Edge >= 90